{
  "stem": "1160.3",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And there wasn't much to do really, because we didn't have anything.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "You know, again, we had that little bit of sugar.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] but when we walk into this room, what fascinated me again-- always find something fascinating-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] wooden parquet, shiny, and the sun.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And there is a big window it comes through.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It's a very pretty picture, very empty.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "There was nothing but my grandmother against the wall on the floor.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But the floor was very pretty, so I noticed this.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Well, I don't know how long we were here.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But I like the idea there was a-- the windows were low.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And facing the pool, there was also a window.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And I look out on that window, and it was very interesting.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I always like to watch people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And there I see from the other side there comes a mother and two daughters.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "It's very-- I noticed them right away because they seemed to me very tall and very good-looking.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "They were pretty people, but so big.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I see them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I said, what are they doing?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They had a-- a scarf, [INAUDIBLE], like a blanket, not even-- a blanket, but a pretty blanket, a colorful one, they have in their hand.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I said, I wonder what they are going to do.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You see, I could always within my mind-- I could always entertain myself.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I-- We'll have to pick up.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I shouldn't forget this.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I just--",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
